6 An Act relating to civil procedure; amending 12 O.S.
2021, Section 131, which relates to venue;
7 establishing proper venue for certain actions; and
providing an effective date.
8
9
10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
11 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 12 O.S. 2021, Section 131, is
12 amended to read as follows:
13 Section 131. Except as provided in Section 132 of this title or
14 Section 163 of Title 51 of the Oklahoma Statutes:
15 1. Actions for the following causes shall be brought in the
16 county in which the subject of the action is situated:
17 a. for the recovery of real property, or of any estate,
18 or interest therein, or the determination in any form
19 of any such right or interest,
20 b. for the partition of real property,
21 c. for the sale of real property under a mortgage, lien,
22 or other encumbrance or charge, and
23
